org.project

Class TreeStorage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.project.TreeStorage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TokensStorage

    public final class TreeStorage
extends java.lang.Object
implements TokensStorage
    This class is used to keep the tokens associated with their frequency in insertion operations. It inserts tokens and orders them based on their frequencies. It has few more features such as removing all tokens, printing them, printing a given token frequency.
